{"tid":1776273,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕唔想誤食美心不如自己做搞手","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T18:10:21.000Z","uid":97120,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5eaf29f36d5798d7d913f095bb400f4de8bd44f","tid":1776273,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"港豬特色 又懶又嫌麻煩<br />\n有得食有得玩就得 所以元氣呢d仆街深藍店先仲有人幫襯<br />\n<br />\n趁聖誕節 大家身邊都會有公司藍豬 朋友港豬 話要搞party 買野食<br />\n雖然無心情但既然避唔到 點解唔將呢d錢幫襯黃店？<br />\n要幫港豬藍豬d錢消費係同路人身上<br />\n首先要<br />\n自 己 做 搞 手<br />\n主動book到會 book party house<br />\n有咁黃揀咁黃 令到d黃店有咁爆得咁爆<br />\n黃色經濟圈咁又注左一大筆資金落去 又唔洗幫襯到藍店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/janP6E1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjanP6E1.png&h=a4fe6f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經有人整左黃店到會list 跟住book就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgoodwest_standwithhk&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=961e7607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少消費既力量 要黃色體系壯大<br />\n手足先可以得到更加多既支援<br />\n被捕手足都要有工返去維持生活<br />\n你每日洗錢習慣都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f90af4767f175680aff3cca7ffbef71acc9bd9","tid":1776273,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c216291a928d2ce17e1d8d0afbd6afa990b5b4","tid":1776273,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor